WEBVTT

01:25.710 --> 01:35.020
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.330 --> 01:37.910
[Episode 18]

01:38.200 --> 01:40.450
So what did you figure out?

01:41.150 --> 01:43.570
It turns out
that my dad's roommates include

01:43.570 --> 01:45.890
a singer, a musician,

01:46.070 --> 01:47.130
a big star,

01:47.570 --> 01:49.729
a great scriptwriter for movies,

01:49.810 --> 01:50.940
and a great painter.

01:52.039 --> 01:53.789
There are so many people doing big things.

01:53.789 --> 01:56.920
I've never seen any
in the county or the village.

01:54.970 --> 02:02.480
[Endeavor]

01:57.710 --> 01:59.850
Dad, I understand now.

02:00.420 --> 02:02.480
This is the real grandeur of Beijing.

02:03.710 --> 02:05.810
That's my boy! Well said!

02:12.360 --> 02:12.860
Dad.

02:13.240 --> 02:15.030
Today, I want everyone here

02:15.240 --> 02:16.360
to be my witnesses.

02:16.840 --> 02:18.690
I will go back and study hard.

02:19.090 --> 02:20.430
When I take the college entrance exam,

02:20.430 --> 02:22.030
I'll definitely
get into a university in Beijing.

02:22.030 --> 02:23.970
Great, we'll wait for you in Beijing.

02:23.970 --> 02:25.829
We'll all wait for you in Beijing.

02:26.180 --> 02:27.630
Come, cheers.

02:29.960 --> 02:31.050
Come on, come on.

02:31.130 --> 02:32.250
Sit down.

02:32.310 --> 02:33.090
Hurry and take a seat.

02:33.090 --> 02:34.400
We've been waiting for you for ages!

02:34.400 --> 02:35.079
Pour the wine.

02:35.079 --> 02:36.680
It's freezing cold outside.

02:38.680 --> 02:39.250
When did you leave?

02:39.250 --> 02:41.050
Come on, let me scratch his back.

02:41.190 --> 02:42.079
Cold! Cold!

02:42.650 --> 02:43.380
It's so cold.

02:43.870 --> 02:45.130
I'm freezing!

02:45.180 --> 02:47.110
Come on, eat up. Take a seat and eat.

02:47.310 --> 02:47.810
Come on.

02:49.130 --> 02:50.150
That's good.

02:51.010 --> 02:52.140
Mr. Guo, Mrs. Jiang,

02:52.750 --> 02:53.930
I just

02:53.960 --> 02:55.370
tidied up a vacant room for you.

02:55.370 --> 02:57.020
Before the Spring Festival,
your family of three

02:57.020 --> 02:58.440
can stay at the Seasons Change Hostel.

02:58.440 --> 02:59.170
Is that okay?

03:00.020 --> 03:01.460
Over there, we...

03:01.520 --> 03:02.590
-Nice!
-Good!

03:02.630 --> 03:03.930
-It's good.
-Brilliant.

03:03.930 --> 03:04.560
From now on,

03:04.560 --> 03:05.580
we can enjoy
Mrs. Jiang's cooking every day!

03:05.580 --> 03:06.370
-Right?
-Yeah.

03:06.370 --> 03:07.170
Amazing food.

03:08.460 --> 03:10.040
Mrs. Jiang says thank you.

03:10.080 --> 03:11.420
Come on, just eat up.

03:11.530 --> 03:13.130
We've been talking too much.

03:25.800 --> 03:28.290
[Seasons Change Hostel]

03:34.310 --> 03:34.900
Ranran,

03:36.430 --> 03:37.829
can I go in and take a look?

03:38.130 --> 03:39.530
It's quite messy inside.

03:47.910 --> 03:49.170
Actually, I just want

03:49.200 --> 03:50.800
to reminisce about my youth.

03:58.990 --> 04:03.440
[Seasons Change Hostel]

04:10.410 --> 04:11.190
Back then,

04:11.410 --> 04:13.710
I also lived
in this kind of hutong in Beijing.

04:13.710 --> 04:14.870
I remember the landlord

04:14.870 --> 04:15.470
renovated

04:15.470 --> 04:16.750
a very small room,

04:17.180 --> 04:18.440
with only a mat inside,

04:19.329 --> 04:20.329
and no furniture.

04:20.329 --> 04:21.190
My daily necessities,

04:21.190 --> 04:22.220
pots, and pans were

04:22.220 --> 04:23.550
all placed on the floor.

04:24.240 --> 04:25.040
In winter,

04:25.310 --> 04:27.130
it was so cold
that I didn't even dare get out of bed.

04:27.130 --> 04:28.930
In summer, it was scorching hot.

04:29.180 --> 04:30.510
Which way should we go?

04:31.010 --> 04:31.650
That way.

04:52.010 --> 04:53.180
I got up in the morning,

04:53.180 --> 04:54.210
had breakfast,

04:54.510 --> 04:55.500
and dressed myself up

04:55.500 --> 04:56.430
to look sharp...

04:56.750 --> 04:57.950
Ranran, you're back.

05:00.800 --> 05:02.730
Then I combed my hair really nicely

05:02.830 --> 05:04.450
and went out to talk business.

05:04.450 --> 05:05.620
Guess what?

05:06.040 --> 05:06.800
After hours of talking,

05:06.800 --> 05:08.660
I didn't even close a single deal.

05:11.270 --> 05:12.860
Mr. Chu, so you...

05:14.540 --> 05:15.400
Used to be poor?

05:16.740 --> 05:18.100
Who's never been poor?

05:19.360 --> 05:21.160
But poor as I was, I had ambition.

05:21.420 --> 05:23.050
At that time, I swore to myself

05:23.050 --> 05:23.810
that one day

05:23.810 --> 05:24.870
I would make big bucks,

05:24.870 --> 05:25.930
drive a luxury car,

05:26.270 --> 05:27.200
use a cell phone,

05:27.600 --> 05:29.060
and stay in luxury hotels.

05:29.310 --> 05:29.910
Of course,

05:30.240 --> 05:32.240
none of these is a big deal now.

05:30.570 --> 05:34.710
[Seasons Change Hostel]

05:34.780 --> 05:36.390
You are going back
to Huzhou for the New Year.

05:36.390 --> 05:37.990
Have you bought your ticket?

05:38.010 --> 05:38.630
Yes.

05:40.250 --> 05:41.780
Do you need any help from me?

05:43.659 --> 05:44.080
Okay.

05:47.000 --> 05:48.310
Now that you know

05:48.460 --> 05:50.260
I recommended you for this role,

05:50.630 --> 05:51.890
will you still play it?

05:57.190 --> 05:57.659
I will.

05:59.450 --> 06:00.930
I want to prove myself

06:00.950 --> 06:02.130
and prove that you introduced them

06:02.130 --> 06:02.960
to a good actress,

06:02.960 --> 06:03.750
not a fool

06:03.750 --> 06:04.830
who can't act.

06:05.430 --> 06:06.810
I want them to thank you,

06:07.250 --> 06:08.850
so you don't owe them a favor.

06:10.070 --> 06:10.540
Good.

06:11.340 --> 06:12.070
I'll look forward

06:12.070 --> 06:13.740
to your wonderful performance,

06:13.740 --> 06:14.770
so they'll all come

06:14.770 --> 06:16.830
to thank me with sincerity one by one.

06:22.630 --> 06:23.770
I won't walk you inside,

06:23.770 --> 06:25.170
lest I cause you trouble.

06:29.130 --> 06:29.660
Bye-bye.

06:30.740 --> 06:31.270
Goodbye.

07:04.820 --> 07:07.290
[Seasons Change Hostel]

07:29.930 --> 07:39.100
[Seasons Change Hostel]

07:50.340 --> 07:52.159
Why are you zoning out?

07:53.070 --> 07:55.060
Zhang's wife was asking me

07:55.220 --> 07:56.659
if you had finished repairing

07:56.659 --> 07:57.310
Zhang's watch.

07:57.310 --> 07:58.890
They need it for the New Year.

07:58.890 --> 07:59.770
I'm fixing it.

08:00.810 --> 08:01.600
Come on.

08:06.490 --> 08:08.020
What date is New Year's Eve?

08:08.570 --> 08:09.220
No idea.

08:14.600 --> 08:15.600
I'm wondering...

08:16.780 --> 08:17.740
Did we

08:18.660 --> 08:20.550
forget something?

08:21.950 --> 08:22.750
I have no idea.

08:23.430 --> 08:24.430
You figure it out.

08:26.610 --> 08:28.870
Maybe it's the recent temperature drop?

08:29.920 --> 08:31.180
Why does it feel

08:31.180 --> 08:33.500
so cold and so empty

08:34.150 --> 08:35.380
in our house?

08:36.970 --> 08:39.000
What's wrong with you a-again?

08:39.010 --> 08:39.740
Why are you laughing?

08:39.740 --> 08:40.770
No, I mean,

08:40.860 --> 08:41.750
just look at you.

08:41.750 --> 08:43.890
Look at your habit of not being honest
with what you really want.

08:43.890 --> 08:45.510
If you want to call your son

08:45.510 --> 08:47.170
to ask him when he's buying the ticket

08:47.170 --> 08:48.200
and if he's coming back for the New Year,

08:48.200 --> 08:49.740
just go make a call.

08:49.760 --> 08:51.600
You're the one missing your son,

08:51.650 --> 08:53.150
and you're dragging me into it.

08:53.150 --> 08:54.600
You go ahead and call him.

08:54.620 --> 08:55.460
Call him if you want.

08:55.460 --> 08:56.860
Why make it sound like I...

08:56.860 --> 08:58.520
Did I provoke you? Spare me...

08:58.600 --> 09:01.730
Yeah, yeah, I'm missing him
and going to call him. Man...

09:02.060 --> 09:03.920
No need to look for the phone book.

09:04.130 --> 09:05.300
Just dial directly.

09:05.320 --> 09:06.220
010.

09:07.260 --> 09:10.310
6235 522

09:16.910 --> 09:17.910
Northeasterner?

09:18.920 --> 09:20.720
This is Shengli's mom speaking.

09:20.910 --> 09:21.870
Yes.

09:22.000 --> 09:23.250
Happy New Year!

09:31.870 --> 09:32.670
Pair of fours.

09:33.750 --> 09:35.550
Where are Xiaobao and your wife?

09:35.650 --> 09:36.710
They went shopping

09:37.290 --> 09:39.100
to buy stuff for the family.

09:39.120 --> 09:41.010
Liangliang kept me here

09:41.320 --> 09:42.150
to play cards with him.

09:42.150 --> 09:44.080
Xu Shengli, there's a call for you.

09:46.400 --> 09:47.730
Your mom's on the phone.

09:48.980 --> 09:49.610
Hands off.

09:49.820 --> 09:52.420
You tried to peek at his cards
as soon as he left?

09:53.250 --> 09:54.310
-Your turn.
-Guys.

09:54.790 --> 09:56.190
It's almost the New Year.

09:56.750 --> 09:57.600
When are you leaving?

09:57.600 --> 09:58.320
Come with me to register,

09:58.320 --> 09:59.580
so I can wrap up my work.

10:00.390 --> 10:01.320
Whose turn is it?

10:01.530 --> 10:02.090
My turn.

10:02.250 --> 10:03.020
Pair of tens.

10:03.860 --> 10:05.500
Clear. Pair of jacks.

10:06.390 --> 10:07.220
I'll register the 28th

10:07.220 --> 10:08.870
of the New Year's first month.

10:08.870 --> 10:09.620
Our family of three

10:09.620 --> 10:11.770
will stay and have fun in Beijing
for a few more days.

10:11.770 --> 10:13.370
Pair of jacks. Pair of jacks.

10:13.370 --> 10:14.460
Register mine, too.

10:14.460 --> 10:15.410
I'm leaving a day earlier than Zongbao.

10:15.410 --> 10:16.080
The 27th.

10:16.200 --> 10:17.060
Pair of queens.

10:18.120 --> 10:18.980
What about you?

10:21.080 --> 10:21.930
I'm asking you.

10:21.930 --> 10:22.810
Play.

10:22.940 --> 10:23.360
You...

10:24.370 --> 10:25.770
If you don't play, I will.

10:27.110 --> 10:28.910
Pair of twos, and a little joker.

10:29.850 --> 10:30.660
Stick it on.

10:32.260 --> 10:34.540
Why are you the only one
getting these stuck on?

10:34.540 --> 10:36.000
Come on, you stay. Come on.

10:36.320 --> 10:37.180
One more round.

10:43.040 --> 10:43.830
Hello, Mom.

10:44.690 --> 10:45.560
Shengli,

10:46.390 --> 10:48.670
well, are you doing okay?

10:48.670 --> 10:49.550
I'm doing pretty well.

10:49.550 --> 10:50.670
I just want to know

10:50.790 --> 10:53.240
if you've bought your ticket
for the Spring Festival.

10:53.240 --> 10:54.080
Around the Spring Festival,

10:54.080 --> 10:56.080
tickets are hard to get nationwide.

10:56.080 --> 10:57.460
Mom, just rest assured.

10:57.460 --> 10:59.190
I already bought it in advance.

11:00.620 --> 11:01.250
Great!

11:01.250 --> 11:02.080
Okay, then.

11:02.470 --> 11:04.190
So, tell your dad

11:04.220 --> 11:05.950
which day and which train it is.

11:07.410 --> 11:07.820
Okay.

11:08.370 --> 11:08.840
Answer it,

11:08.840 --> 11:09.700
or I'll hang up.

11:13.410 --> 11:15.090
Look at you! You always do it this way.

11:15.090 --> 11:16.230
Fine, then.

11:17.770 --> 11:18.430
Hello, Dad.

11:19.530 --> 11:20.530
I'm telling you,

11:20.890 --> 11:22.890
watch your belongings on the train.

11:24.840 --> 11:26.650
Well, my train will leave on the 25th,

11:26.650 --> 11:27.960
at about 7 a.m.,

11:27.980 --> 11:29.100
and I'll arrive in Yantai.

11:29.100 --> 11:30.620
Then I'll be home in half an hour.

11:30.620 --> 11:31.350
Got it.

11:39.800 --> 11:40.640
I see.

11:41.530 --> 11:43.010
"Got it"? What did you get?

11:43.030 --> 11:45.010
You haven't even asked him
which day he's coming back.

11:45.010 --> 11:46.070
I got it!

11:46.910 --> 11:47.600
Jeez!

11:48.720 --> 11:50.150
This guy. Good grief.

11:50.960 --> 11:52.090
Where are you going?

11:52.510 --> 11:53.910
To buy some goods for the New Year.

11:53.910 --> 11:54.840
Where am I going?

11:55.910 --> 11:57.170
Goods for the New Year.

11:58.870 --> 11:59.530
If you're not going,

11:59.530 --> 12:01.330
what do you expect me to pay with?

12:01.410 --> 12:02.250
You don't have money, right?

12:02.250 --> 12:03.650
Isn't it obvious?

12:04.370 --> 12:06.530
Fine. Let's go buy goods for the New Year.

12:06.530 --> 12:07.510
Jeez...

12:07.670 --> 12:08.340
Let's go.

12:10.270 --> 12:11.070
Welcome back.

12:13.010 --> 12:14.810
You bought a whole lot of things.

12:17.720 --> 12:18.760
Yeah.

12:19.480 --> 12:20.100
Why do you look

12:20.100 --> 12:21.120
a little gloomy?

12:21.620 --> 12:22.130
These are all

12:22.130 --> 12:23.860
from the list my mom made for me.

12:24.030 --> 12:26.170
They're all
my brother's favorite foods and drinks.

12:26.170 --> 12:27.910
Not a single item can be missing.

12:27.910 --> 12:30.370
I've been to several streets
to get them all.

12:34.320 --> 12:35.220
Why do I feel like

12:35.220 --> 12:37.100
you can't bear to leave me?

12:37.740 --> 12:39.880
Of course I'm reluctant to part with you.

12:39.880 --> 12:41.480
Didn't I leave you my number?

12:41.910 --> 12:43.310
Call me when you get back.

12:44.600 --> 12:47.910
The day Mrs. Jiang and Xiaobao came,

12:48.400 --> 12:50.040
when we were having dinner,

12:50.290 --> 12:52.820
I really envied that kind of happiness.

12:53.550 --> 12:55.060
Don't laugh at me,

12:55.220 --> 12:57.280
but I actually made a wish in my heart.

12:57.620 --> 12:59.120
I wish we could spend

12:59.140 --> 13:01.540
the New Year together
like this every year.

13:01.550 --> 13:02.520
Honestly,

13:02.790 --> 13:03.290
I feel like

13:03.290 --> 13:05.790
the Seasons Change Hostel is
more like my home.

13:05.790 --> 13:07.120
This is indeed our home.

13:09.000 --> 13:10.700
As long as it makes everyone happy,

13:10.700 --> 13:11.500
it is a home.

13:15.510 --> 13:16.040
Alright.

13:16.480 --> 13:18.150
Let's put up these couplets

13:18.150 --> 13:19.270
for our home.

13:20.530 --> 13:21.930
There are couplets, too?

13:22.530 --> 13:24.130
Shengli wrote them. Come on.

13:27.180 --> 13:28.400
How brilliant.

13:28.750 --> 13:29.280
Let's go.

13:33.340 --> 13:34.100
Luo.

13:34.340 --> 13:35.370
This lantern looks

13:35.370 --> 13:36.820
much bigger than last year's.

13:36.820 --> 13:37.910
If it were smaller, I'd be afraid

13:37.910 --> 13:39.320
you couldn't find your way back.

13:39.320 --> 13:40.020
Sublessor,

13:40.130 --> 13:41.960
you are even brighter
than this red lantern.

13:41.960 --> 13:43.080
That sounds

13:43.100 --> 13:45.460
even better
than those New Year's greetings.

13:45.460 --> 13:46.200
Luo, let me steady it for you.

13:46.200 --> 13:47.000
Don't bother.

13:47.000 --> 13:47.670
You guys should get going.

13:47.670 --> 13:48.660
Or you'll miss your train.

13:48.660 --> 13:49.250
Hurry up and go.

13:49.250 --> 13:50.310
All right. Come on.

13:50.360 --> 13:51.720
The doors
of the Seasons Change Hostel will

13:51.720 --> 13:52.840
always be open for you guys.

13:52.840 --> 13:53.400
Okay.

13:53.500 --> 13:54.350
Okay, Luo.

13:54.370 --> 13:56.360
-See you next year.
-Welcome back soon after the New Year.

13:56.360 --> 13:57.220
Happy New Year.

13:57.580 --> 13:59.790
Say hello to your family for me
when you get home.

13:59.790 --> 14:00.990
No problem! Goodbye!

14:02.250 --> 14:03.510
Ranran, Ranran.

14:04.310 --> 14:06.290
Why are you going back so suddenly?

14:06.290 --> 14:08.550
We haven't had a proper talk about us yet.

14:09.480 --> 14:10.720
What time is your train?

14:10.720 --> 14:11.790
How about we find a small restaurant

14:11.790 --> 14:12.870
and sit down for a chat?

14:12.870 --> 14:14.240
Let's just talk.

14:16.720 --> 14:19.050
There's nothing to talk about between us.

14:37.360 --> 14:39.290
Happy Spring Festival in advance.

14:53.650 --> 14:54.290
All set.

14:54.600 --> 14:55.060
Come on.

14:57.370 --> 14:58.290
Let's split them.

14:58.290 --> 14:58.860
Okay.

14:59.390 --> 15:01.500
You take 3 boxes of Daoxiangcun pastries.

15:01.500 --> 15:01.940
Your mom said

15:01.940 --> 15:03.870
she likes the jujube paste pastry.

15:04.240 --> 15:05.880
We agreed on 2 boxes each.

15:06.170 --> 15:07.120
It's fine.

15:07.910 --> 15:10.040
She's fond of the jujube paste pastry!

15:10.250 --> 15:11.980
One box is enough for my family.

15:13.120 --> 15:15.100
Alright, thank you on behalf of my mom.

15:15.100 --> 15:15.760
No problem.

15:17.360 --> 15:18.020
And this.

15:18.220 --> 15:19.880
My mom specially sent it over.

15:19.910 --> 15:21.440
It's her handmade sausage.

15:22.440 --> 15:23.510
Take it home and try it.

15:23.510 --> 15:24.840
If you like it,

15:25.200 --> 15:26.220
there are also cured ribs,

15:26.220 --> 15:27.120
cured ham, cured duck wings,

15:27.120 --> 15:27.870
and so much more.

15:27.870 --> 15:28.400
I like it!

15:28.860 --> 15:30.050
You haven't even tasted it yet.

15:30.050 --> 15:30.840
I just love it.

15:30.840 --> 15:31.910
My family likes it, too.

15:31.910 --> 15:33.080
I'm speaking for them.

15:33.080 --> 15:34.650
If so, you can have as much as you like.

15:34.650 --> 15:35.080
Okay.

15:39.740 --> 15:41.470
Alright, everything's ready.

15:42.510 --> 15:43.840
There's one more thing.

15:43.940 --> 15:44.770
What else?

15:48.910 --> 15:49.730
Who is it for?

15:49.960 --> 15:50.690
It's for you.

15:50.840 --> 15:52.100
Open it and take a look.

15:55.960 --> 15:56.960
A New Year's gift?

16:02.410 --> 16:03.200
The number is

16:03.200 --> 16:05.780
126, extension 2935092.

16:06.290 --> 16:07.130
Tell your family

16:07.130 --> 16:08.320
this number when you go back.

16:08.320 --> 16:09.120
You'll know immediately

16:09.120 --> 16:10.720
if anyone wants to reach you.

16:12.310 --> 16:14.200
I'll get a pen to write it down for you.

16:14.200 --> 16:14.830
Hold on.

16:24.980 --> 16:25.910
Write with this.

16:27.890 --> 16:28.720
Hero?

16:29.770 --> 16:32.870
Is... Is this... for me?

16:39.650 --> 16:40.580
Write it on this.

16:41.120 --> 16:41.860
Let me try.

16:50.040 --> 16:52.270
[126, extension 2935092]

16:52.700 --> 16:54.160
This pen is really smooth.

16:55.680 --> 16:57.410
Then use it every day from now on

16:57.410 --> 16:59.210
to write scripts, good scripts.

17:00.620 --> 17:02.350
I'll also use it to write you...

17:02.670 --> 17:03.870
w-write you letters.

17:05.280 --> 17:07.339
Are you good at writing love letters?

17:09.200 --> 17:11.700
I've never written a love letter.

17:11.730 --> 17:12.190
Well,

17:12.510 --> 17:13.660
but I'm a screenwriter!

17:13.660 --> 17:15.109
I... I can compose it.

17:16.990 --> 17:17.849
Where is yours?

17:19.619 --> 17:20.619
I only bought one.

17:22.119 --> 17:22.900
Finally,

17:22.900 --> 17:24.180
we have a communication tool,

17:24.180 --> 17:25.180
but it's one-way?

17:25.880 --> 17:27.210
Only you can contact me?

17:27.230 --> 17:28.079
Well,

17:28.210 --> 17:29.780
one of these isn't cheap.

17:30.050 --> 17:31.420
Besides, you're a girl.

17:31.420 --> 17:32.740
If you can be reached at any time,

17:32.740 --> 17:35.070
we'll feel more at ease, right?

17:51.220 --> 17:53.710
[Yantai]

17:53.880 --> 17:54.830
Shengli, you're back!

17:54.830 --> 17:55.330
Hi, madam.

17:55.330 --> 17:56.250
Back for the New Year?

17:56.250 --> 17:57.040
Yes.

18:16.030 --> 18:17.360
What are you looking at?

18:17.620 --> 18:18.750
Don't recognize me?

18:22.560 --> 18:23.490
Let's go inside.

18:33.310 --> 18:34.050
Hua.

18:34.980 --> 18:36.050
Our son is back.

18:39.010 --> 18:39.660
Mom!

18:41.540 --> 18:42.800
My son is back!

18:45.660 --> 18:47.300
Let Mom hug you.

18:47.930 --> 18:49.060
I missed you so much.

18:49.300 --> 18:50.300
Let me look at you.

18:51.700 --> 18:52.610
Why did you lose weight?

18:52.610 --> 18:53.570
I didn't!

18:53.590 --> 18:54.180
Did you

18:54.180 --> 18:55.180
not eat well in Beijing?

18:55.180 --> 18:56.110
I ate very well!

18:56.110 --> 18:57.770
I ate a lot in Beijing!

18:57.770 --> 18:59.030
My heart aches for you.

18:59.050 --> 19:00.910
Mom, I really didn't lose weight.

19:01.010 --> 19:01.500
My heart aches.

19:01.500 --> 19:02.500
Alright, enough.

19:03.740 --> 19:05.140
Is the food ready?

19:05.200 --> 19:06.030
It's ready.

19:06.090 --> 19:07.070
I only need to take it out of the pot.

19:07.070 --> 19:07.980
Hurry up.

19:08.270 --> 19:09.290
Take off your coat

19:09.290 --> 19:10.060
and have some water.

19:10.060 --> 19:10.420
Okay.

19:10.460 --> 19:11.660
It will be ready soon.

19:19.090 --> 19:20.640
Look how happy your mom is.

19:21.230 --> 19:23.700
[Wenzhou]

19:25.640 --> 19:26.610
It's so good to be home.

19:26.610 --> 19:27.610
Missed home, huh?

19:28.590 --> 19:29.640
I missed my mom.

19:33.790 --> 19:34.240
Come on.

19:34.060 --> 19:36.270
[Huzhou]

19:34.240 --> 19:35.870
Mom, I'm back!

19:36.070 --> 19:37.720
You're back so early!

19:37.770 --> 19:39.830
Hello, Mrs. Zhang, Mrs. Wang, Mr. Li.

19:40.460 --> 19:41.380
This tile...

19:42.140 --> 19:43.000
I win.

19:44.330 --> 19:45.110
You win?

19:45.850 --> 19:48.050
You've been the only one
winning the whole time.

19:48.050 --> 19:49.050
You're back, sis!

19:49.310 --> 19:50.130
I'm back.

19:50.310 --> 19:51.140
Help me carry some.

19:51.140 --> 19:52.410
Are these all for me?

20:03.780 --> 20:06.420
[Shanxi]

20:27.550 --> 20:27.980
Dad.

20:29.730 --> 20:30.410
Son,

20:31.190 --> 20:31.920
you're back.

20:43.670 --> 20:46.050
[Henan]

20:48.590 --> 20:49.500
We're home!

20:49.500 --> 20:51.030
We're home for the New Year!

21:11.970 --> 21:13.170
What brings you here?

21:15.010 --> 21:16.210
You're having a meal?

21:16.940 --> 21:18.870
I'm here to add some dishes for you.

21:18.940 --> 21:19.850
I brought you

21:19.850 --> 21:20.960
hot dumplings

21:21.440 --> 21:22.700
and a big pork knuckle.

21:23.320 --> 21:25.250
We should eat well for the New Year.

21:27.270 --> 21:28.550
I thought you had gone back

21:28.550 --> 21:30.350
to your hometown
after we had a meal last week.

21:30.350 --> 21:31.840
Close the door.

21:31.860 --> 21:32.990
Don't you feel cold?

21:34.880 --> 21:36.050
T-Then you...

21:39.530 --> 21:40.760
What do you mean?

21:44.410 --> 21:46.370
If you don't want me here,

21:46.400 --> 21:46.960
I'll leave.

21:46.960 --> 21:48.400
No, no, I...

21:54.940 --> 21:56.140
Take off your coat.

21:56.170 --> 21:58.370
It's letting the remaining cold air in.

21:58.940 --> 21:59.850
Take a seat.

22:02.900 --> 22:03.760
It's still hot.

22:05.070 --> 22:06.130
Is it cold outside?

22:06.400 --> 22:07.630
Freezing cold.

22:09.790 --> 22:11.590
You even brought the little pot.

22:11.790 --> 22:13.650
Be careful, don't burn yourself.

22:18.200 --> 22:19.530
This huge pork knuckle!

22:20.330 --> 22:21.370
Not bad, right?

22:22.170 --> 22:23.030
It's great.

22:25.460 --> 22:27.060
You haven't answered me yet.

22:27.220 --> 22:28.200
It's the New Year,

22:28.200 --> 22:29.090
and you didn't go back home.

22:29.090 --> 22:30.290
What brings you here?

22:32.380 --> 22:33.590
My home is far away.

22:33.920 --> 22:35.640
My parents are doing alright

22:35.640 --> 22:36.640
at home together.

22:37.610 --> 22:40.060
I'm also used to being alone.

22:41.030 --> 22:42.290
Aren't you alone, too?

22:43.310 --> 22:44.050
I don't have any relatives left

22:44.050 --> 22:45.850
in my hometown in the Northeast.

22:48.640 --> 22:49.530
My parents passed away

22:49.530 --> 22:50.790
when I was very little.

22:51.660 --> 22:52.990
I'm actually an orphan.

22:53.680 --> 22:55.810
When I first came to Beijing by myself,

22:56.070 --> 22:57.660
it was the boss
of this Seasons Change Hostel

22:57.660 --> 22:58.460
who took me in.

22:59.570 --> 23:01.370
I treat this place as my own home.

23:02.510 --> 23:03.970
I treat them all as family.

23:05.420 --> 23:06.940
But when the New Year comes,

23:06.940 --> 23:08.090
they all go home.

23:09.330 --> 23:10.160
I'm used to it.

23:17.300 --> 23:18.050
Lili.

23:20.440 --> 23:21.290
The past few times we met,

23:21.290 --> 23:23.420
there was something I didn't tell you.

23:24.420 --> 23:26.180
This hostel looks quite big, right?

23:26.180 --> 23:27.710
Actually, I'm not the boss.

23:29.200 --> 23:30.840
I'm just a worker

23:30.920 --> 23:32.850
to look after the shop for the boss.

23:38.630 --> 23:40.450
No one's taken you for the boss.

23:40.980 --> 23:42.910
You've never taken me for the boss?

23:43.720 --> 23:45.010
I like to show off a bit

23:45.030 --> 23:46.290
in front of the others.

23:48.070 --> 23:49.670
But I don't want to lie to you.

23:56.500 --> 23:58.030
Now that I've made it clear,

23:58.610 --> 23:59.850
I feel relieved.

24:01.290 --> 24:03.940
You feel relieved, and then?

24:05.090 --> 24:06.700
Then you can just ask me whatever else

24:06.700 --> 24:07.400
you want to know.

24:07.400 --> 24:08.860
I'll tell you everything.

24:11.500 --> 24:12.730
Hurry up and eat.

24:12.900 --> 24:14.760
We have plenty of time ahead of us.

24:16.250 --> 24:17.040
Really?

24:33.110 --> 24:35.010
I'll go close the front door.

24:36.030 --> 24:38.030
The Seasons Change Hostel is
celebrating the New Year!

24:38.030 --> 24:40.340
Well... This is...

24:45.310 --> 24:46.700
The last dish is coming.

24:47.250 --> 24:47.910
Here you go.

24:52.480 --> 24:53.570
I put it on.

24:53.640 --> 24:54.310
Isn't it nice?

24:54.310 --> 24:55.770
It looks great on you, Mom.

24:56.200 --> 24:56.770
It looks good.

24:56.770 --> 24:58.030
Look at my son's taste.

24:58.090 --> 24:58.920
It's so good.

24:58.940 --> 25:00.700
It's both beautiful and festive.

25:00.700 --> 25:01.780
It suits you so well.

25:01.780 --> 25:02.720
Thank you, son.

25:04.150 --> 25:05.000
Why don't you wear yours?

25:05.000 --> 25:06.200
Our son bought one for you, too.

25:06.200 --> 25:07.940
Me? If I wore it, you'd cook?

25:08.050 --> 25:09.650
Who'd go cook in the kitchen?

25:09.880 --> 25:12.030
Your dad is treasuring it so much.

25:12.070 --> 25:13.090
Then wear it tomorrow.

25:13.090 --> 25:14.890
Wear it when you're not cooking.

25:15.270 --> 25:16.820
Son, you know what?

25:17.030 --> 25:18.110
These dishes were

25:19.810 --> 25:21.310
all prepared by your dad.

25:21.600 --> 25:22.220
Your dad's been

25:22.220 --> 25:23.680
preparing
for tonight's New Year's Eve dinner

25:23.680 --> 25:25.440
for quite a long time.

25:26.760 --> 25:27.990
He cooked them all.

25:39.200 --> 25:40.790
Dad, Mom.

25:42.070 --> 25:43.130
Over the past half year,

25:43.130 --> 25:44.590
I was drifting in Beijing,

25:45.240 --> 25:46.440
making you two worry.

25:46.530 --> 25:47.930
This first glass of wine,

25:48.770 --> 25:50.100
I'd like to toast to you.

25:50.560 --> 25:53.400
We won't be worried after New Year's Eve?

25:54.810 --> 25:57.070
You've only been in Beijing
for a short time.

25:57.070 --> 25:58.870
How did you start drinking wine?

25:59.750 --> 26:00.140
I...

26:00.160 --> 26:01.600
It's New Year's Eve!

26:02.050 --> 26:02.970
We're having fun!

26:02.970 --> 26:03.920
Even I want to have a drink, too.

26:03.920 --> 26:04.820
Son, go ahead.

26:04.850 --> 26:05.980
Pour me a glass, too.

26:06.220 --> 26:07.010
No more soft drinks.

26:07.010 --> 26:08.000
Mom, have this one.

26:08.000 --> 26:08.730
Wait, you...

26:08.770 --> 26:09.300
Alright.

26:09.610 --> 26:10.070
Come on.

26:11.780 --> 26:12.700
Come on, son.

26:13.000 --> 26:14.500
I wish you greater progress

26:14.500 --> 26:16.360
in the new year!

26:17.400 --> 26:18.050
Hurry.

26:18.660 --> 26:19.200
Fine, fine.

26:19.200 --> 26:20.030
Your son is toasting you.

26:20.030 --> 26:20.500
Come on.

26:20.500 --> 26:21.560
Stand up, stand up.

26:22.000 --> 26:24.790
-Come on. Let's have a drink together.
-Happy New Year.

26:24.790 --> 26:26.270
Let's get better and better
in the new year.

26:26.270 --> 26:27.530
Get better and better.

26:41.070 --> 26:42.130
This second glass,

26:42.130 --> 26:43.930
Dad, I'd like to toast to you.

26:44.850 --> 26:45.330
Well,

26:45.350 --> 26:47.580
thanks to your goading back then,

26:47.840 --> 26:49.200
it made me burn my bridges

26:49.200 --> 26:50.330
and fight with my back to the wall.

26:50.330 --> 26:51.860
I didn't force you to leave.

26:52.980 --> 26:54.940
You insisted on leaving yourself.

26:55.420 --> 26:57.220
Alright, stop acting so tough.

26:57.440 --> 26:58.940
My son's name is listed

26:58.940 --> 27:00.770
right after the great screenwriter's.

27:00.770 --> 27:02.270
It's really something worth celebrating.

27:02.270 --> 27:03.130
Come on, son...

27:03.770 --> 27:04.810
You haven't poured wine for your dad yet.

27:04.810 --> 27:05.940
Hurry up and pour it.

27:06.270 --> 27:07.400
You're too nervous.

27:09.540 --> 27:09.940
Okay.

27:09.940 --> 27:12.470
Mom, we haven't even
started shooting it yet.

27:12.620 --> 27:14.450
The fact that they paid you is

27:14.650 --> 27:16.180
a recognition of your work.

27:16.290 --> 27:17.220
They'll shoot it

27:17.220 --> 27:18.500
sooner or later.

27:18.510 --> 27:19.700
Come on, congratulations.

27:19.700 --> 27:20.510
Congratulations!

27:20.510 --> 27:21.880
Congratulations!

27:22.590 --> 27:23.450
It's good news.

27:31.550 --> 27:32.660
You've grown up.

27:34.320 --> 27:35.450
Son, you know what?

27:35.490 --> 27:36.940
Your dad once told me,

27:37.770 --> 27:38.820
"In the future,

27:38.850 --> 27:39.900
when our son's movie is

27:39.900 --> 27:40.790
released

27:40.790 --> 27:41.800
in theaters,

27:41.980 --> 27:43.200
I will take

27:43.200 --> 27:44.240
all the relatives we know

27:44.240 --> 27:45.100
to go watch it

27:45.180 --> 27:45.880
and point

27:45.880 --> 27:47.030
to the name on the screen and say,

27:47.030 --> 27:48.770
'Look, that's my son!'"

27:48.810 --> 27:50.160
Alright... Enough.

27:50.200 --> 27:51.510
Come on, stop it.

27:52.170 --> 27:53.350
We haven't started eating the dishes,

27:53.350 --> 27:55.370
yet we've already had
several glasses of wine.

27:55.370 --> 27:55.940
When will you

27:55.940 --> 27:56.900
finish talking?

27:57.070 --> 27:58.250
Isn't it time for us to eat now?

27:58.250 --> 27:59.450
I'm just happy.

27:59.570 --> 28:00.590
Happy, happy.

28:00.860 --> 28:01.420
Mom,

28:01.420 --> 28:02.590
how come I find my dad

28:02.590 --> 28:04.310
much gentler this time I'm back?

28:04.310 --> 28:04.850
Right?

28:06.980 --> 28:08.110
Then how about this?

28:08.420 --> 28:10.090
I'd like to have one last toast.

28:10.090 --> 28:11.680
Right, three toasts, three.

28:11.680 --> 28:12.660
In the new year,

28:13.110 --> 28:14.270
I wish you both

28:14.520 --> 28:15.710
good health

28:16.270 --> 28:17.980
and happiness every day.

28:18.610 --> 28:19.030
Okay.

28:19.140 --> 28:20.690
I wish you both well.

28:20.770 --> 28:21.690
Okay.

28:22.550 --> 28:23.210
Come on.

28:23.230 --> 28:23.900
Cheers.

28:31.790 --> 28:32.290
Come on.

28:32.700 --> 28:33.720
Let's eat up.

28:34.480 --> 28:36.570
We have a great screenwriter
in the family.

28:36.570 --> 28:37.570
Having a New Year's Eve dinner is

28:37.570 --> 28:39.570
almost like acting in a sketch

28:39.610 --> 28:41.210
on the Spring Festival Gala.

28:41.330 --> 28:42.500
Isn't that great?

28:42.500 --> 28:43.830
We are putting on our own show first.

28:43.830 --> 28:45.230
Come on, son. Try this.

28:45.290 --> 28:46.690
Alright, stop drinking.

28:47.000 --> 28:47.830
Have some juice.

28:47.830 --> 28:49.090
You've drunk too much.

28:50.330 --> 28:51.270
Eat more.

28:51.270 --> 28:52.800
Come on, you have some, too.

28:52.810 --> 28:53.430
Okay.

28:53.500 --> 28:53.770
Eat up.

28:53.770 --> 28:54.660
I can reach it.

28:55.000 --> 28:55.960
Look at all these ingredients

28:55.960 --> 28:57.330
your dad bought

28:57.440 --> 28:58.840
from the morning market.

28:59.000 --> 28:59.700
Eat more.

29:01.530 --> 29:02.460
How is it? Take a bite.

29:02.460 --> 29:03.090
Delicious!

29:03.090 --> 29:03.570
Is it good?

29:03.570 --> 29:04.010
Yeah!

29:04.270 --> 29:06.530
How is it compared to your mom's cooking?

29:06.900 --> 29:08.720
It's just that your cooking is
not as good as Mom's.

29:08.720 --> 29:09.320
Right?

29:11.980 --> 29:13.460
Well... alright.

29:13.550 --> 29:13.940
See?

29:13.940 --> 29:15.610
My son is still on my side.

29:21.750 --> 29:22.410
Hey, you...

29:27.440 --> 29:28.570
I want another bowl.

29:30.570 --> 29:32.230
Serve a bowl for your brother.

29:40.080 --> 29:42.010
Sis, didn't you say

29:42.330 --> 29:43.920
you would buy me a pager?

29:44.090 --> 29:45.960
Yeah, I heard it.

29:50.070 --> 29:52.080
Pagers are so expensive.

29:52.240 --> 29:52.790
Didn't I

29:52.790 --> 29:54.270
buy you game cartridges?

29:54.550 --> 29:55.940
A game console is a game console,

29:55.940 --> 29:57.200
and a pager is a pager.

29:57.250 --> 29:58.650
Then give them back to me.

30:05.420 --> 30:07.020
Are you wearing new clothes?

30:08.330 --> 30:09.610
The girl I live with, who's older than me,

30:09.610 --> 30:10.470
lent them to me.

30:11.640 --> 30:12.290
Are there still

30:12.290 --> 30:14.050
such kind girls in the world?

30:15.830 --> 30:16.890
When girls grow up,

30:16.900 --> 30:18.430
they start spending money.

30:18.980 --> 30:20.780
Look how rough my hands are now.

30:22.810 --> 30:25.140
Ever since you were little, I enrolled you

30:25.380 --> 30:26.250
in all sorts of classes

30:26.250 --> 30:28.530
like the eloquence and dance ones.

30:29.660 --> 30:31.190
They were all investments.

30:32.380 --> 30:33.420
You're not thinking

30:33.420 --> 30:34.750
about the family at all.

30:35.380 --> 30:36.000
Mom,

30:36.850 --> 30:38.720
I know things haven't been easy for you,

30:38.720 --> 30:40.250
and I'm making great efforts, too.

30:40.250 --> 30:41.110
Efforts

30:41.550 --> 30:42.980
need to yield results.

30:45.550 --> 30:47.210
What do you mean by "results"?

30:47.590 --> 30:48.240
Money?

30:50.980 --> 30:51.570
Ranran,

30:51.940 --> 30:52.810
let's not talk about

30:52.810 --> 30:53.880
how much I've done for you.

30:53.880 --> 30:55.810
Just look at your younger brother, Fufu.

30:55.810 --> 30:57.070
Didn't he also

30:57.310 --> 30:58.770
give away his college fund

30:58.830 --> 31:02.110
to support your acting in Beijing?

31:03.270 --> 31:06.070
Didn't he fail
the college entrance exam himself?

31:09.400 --> 31:10.550
We are family.

31:10.550 --> 31:12.000
You shouldn't say that.

31:12.110 --> 31:12.790
Right?

31:13.000 --> 31:14.940
Giving goes both ways.

31:15.110 --> 31:17.920
Your brother has a girlfriend now.

31:18.140 --> 31:20.070
You should also take that to heart.

31:22.240 --> 31:22.850
Sis,

31:23.090 --> 31:24.090
when is your TV drama

31:24.090 --> 31:25.140
going to air?

31:26.350 --> 31:27.280
I don't know yet.

31:28.700 --> 31:30.010
Which supporting role are you?

31:30.010 --> 31:30.940
A very minor one.

31:32.090 --> 31:32.940
A minor one?

31:33.140 --> 31:34.330
Can you even be seen?

31:34.500 --> 31:36.430
The scene will flash by in a second.

31:41.000 --> 31:41.550
Mom.

31:43.200 --> 31:44.330
As big as Beijing is,

31:45.440 --> 31:47.300
not everyone there gets a chance.

31:49.380 --> 31:50.380
You must have one.

31:51.220 --> 31:52.550
I'm not pressuring you,

31:52.750 --> 31:55.030
but a woman's beauty
only lasts for a few years.

31:55.030 --> 31:56.490
If you don't work hard now,

31:56.750 --> 31:57.980
what are you waiting for?

31:57.980 --> 31:58.890
Besides,

31:58.960 --> 31:59.750
in a few years,

31:59.750 --> 32:01.440
you'll get married and have kids.

32:01.440 --> 32:01.940
Do you think

32:01.940 --> 32:03.980
you can still chase your dream
of becoming a star?

32:03.980 --> 32:04.980
No way!

32:07.440 --> 32:08.000
Mom,

32:09.420 --> 32:10.550
believe me.

32:11.310 --> 32:12.790
I can be a good actress.

32:13.640 --> 32:15.900
I will... I will work very hard.

32:19.240 --> 32:19.900
Here, Fufu.

32:20.830 --> 32:21.890
Fufu, here you are.

32:23.050 --> 32:23.980
The fish I fried.

32:26.900 --> 32:29.230
Mom, Dad, I wish you good health

32:29.500 --> 32:32.250
and all the best in the new year.

32:32.310 --> 32:32.800
Nice.

32:32.900 --> 32:33.940
Happy New Year.

32:33.940 --> 32:34.550
Yeah.

32:35.640 --> 32:36.500
Happy New Year.

32:36.790 --> 32:37.650
Happy New Year.

32:49.970 --> 32:53.810
♪ That winter snow ♪

32:56.520 --> 33:00.360
♪ Buried all the longing ♪

32:59.310 --> 33:00.710
I will sing a song for you,

33:00.720 --> 33:02.200
"The Ocean, My Hometown."

33:03.810 --> 33:07.440
♪ There's no going back ♪

33:08.240 --> 33:13.250
♪ Luckily, you're here with me ♪

33:18.740 --> 33:25.080
♪ All along the way ♪

33:25.670 --> 33:30.700
♪ Dreams bloom ♪

33:32.340 --> 33:37.310
♪ When starlight meets the sea ♪

33:38.200 --> 33:44.710
♪ I get to know your love ♪

33:45.440 --> 33:50.970
♪ All along the way ♪

33:52.190 --> 33:57.150
♪ Dreams bloom ♪

33:58.600 --> 34:03.750
♪ When the long night ends ♪

34:01.000 --> 34:03.680
This bonfire this year is bigger
than ever.

34:03.790 --> 34:05.290
Prosperous! It's a good omen.

34:04.480 --> 34:13.679
♪ Day is breaking ♪

34:05.660 --> 34:06.410
Have some dumplings.

34:06.410 --> 34:06.900
Kid,

34:07.610 --> 34:08.420
wish you

34:08.989 --> 34:11.110
a booming career in Beijing.

34:19.170 --> 34:21.090
Mom, where is Mr. Ye?

34:21.270 --> 34:23.420
He went to Chen's house
to deliver something.

34:23.420 --> 34:24.400
Their child is 100 days old,

34:24.400 --> 34:26.330
so they ordered 100-family cloth.

34:27.500 --> 34:29.030
Come on, try it.

34:38.010 --> 34:39.610
Shengli went back
to his hometown for the New Year?

34:39.610 --> 34:40.510
"Shengli"?

34:41.380 --> 34:43.909
You're addressing him
in such a friendly way.

34:45.460 --> 34:46.500
He called us

34:46.500 --> 34:48.030
at home many times

34:48.350 --> 34:49.090
and brought you

34:49.090 --> 34:50.420
so much delicious food.

34:50.610 --> 34:51.460
I also paid

34:51.460 --> 34:52.719
for these items, okay?

34:53.690 --> 34:55.590
A few calls, and you've been bought off?

34:55.590 --> 34:56.300
Look at you.

34:56.710 --> 34:58.180
If I didn't like him,

34:59.000 --> 35:00.400
wouldn't you be anxious?

35:01.650 --> 35:02.380
I think you're the one

35:02.380 --> 35:04.040
who's quickly taken his side.

35:04.340 --> 35:05.380
That's because I think

35:05.380 --> 35:06.880
Shengli is a nice guy.

35:07.380 --> 35:08.150
That's why.

35:09.610 --> 35:11.070
You haven't even met him yet.

35:11.070 --> 35:12.330
Yes, I haven't met him.

35:13.440 --> 35:15.010
But I know my daughter well.

35:15.280 --> 35:16.680
I can tell whether you're

35:17.150 --> 35:18.260
doing well or not.

35:23.900 --> 35:25.730
Your daughter is really capable.

35:25.730 --> 35:27.190
I can do fine wherever I go.

35:27.340 --> 35:28.030
Of course.

35:28.320 --> 35:30.570
My daughter has been really something
since childhood.

35:30.570 --> 35:32.170
I know it better than anyone.

35:37.300 --> 35:39.160
But no matter how capable you are,

35:40.260 --> 35:41.190
you'll always be

35:42.170 --> 35:43.530
just a kid to me.

35:45.360 --> 35:47.380
You were out there fighting on your own,

35:47.380 --> 35:48.150
and I was

35:49.130 --> 35:50.330
worried sick as well.

35:51.800 --> 35:52.320
But when I heard

35:52.320 --> 35:53.860
your voice on the phone,

35:54.150 --> 35:54.820
I knew

35:54.940 --> 35:56.400
you were doing well there.

35:57.280 --> 35:58.300
That put my mind

35:58.880 --> 36:00.130
at ease right away.

36:01.300 --> 36:03.270
Later, Shengli called me,

36:03.460 --> 36:04.380
and I knew

36:04.880 --> 36:06.630
someone was taking care of you.

36:07.860 --> 36:09.460
Then he must be a good person.

36:10.480 --> 36:12.010
At least he treats you well.

36:12.230 --> 36:14.090
That is the most important thing.

36:16.880 --> 36:19.110
The people
at the hostel are all so nice to me.

36:19.110 --> 36:19.710
That's because

36:19.710 --> 36:21.190
you are also nice to others.

36:21.190 --> 36:23.090
What goes around comes around.

36:24.320 --> 36:25.850
When you are away from home,

36:26.010 --> 36:27.210
lend a hand to others

36:27.340 --> 36:28.230
when you can.

36:28.940 --> 36:30.200
I've kept that in mind.

36:40.380 --> 36:41.260
It's so good.

36:46.320 --> 36:47.730
I don't know how Xu Shengli

36:47.730 --> 36:48.420
got to know

36:48.420 --> 36:49.570
that you like this.

36:53.530 --> 36:54.210
That day,

36:54.630 --> 36:56.170
he called for an interview

36:57.130 --> 36:59.400
and got sidetracked.

36:59.570 --> 37:01.460
He asked many things about our family

37:01.460 --> 37:01.900
and also asked

37:01.900 --> 37:03.300
about Mr. Ye's health.

37:04.050 --> 37:04.820
Then I got it.

37:06.190 --> 37:06.860
Actually,

37:07.530 --> 37:08.860
he was caring about you.

37:12.710 --> 37:13.910
That's just how he is.

37:14.630 --> 37:15.510
He really looks out

37:15.510 --> 37:16.790
for everyone.

37:17.980 --> 37:20.040
Then you should take good care of him.

37:20.060 --> 37:20.900
Control

37:22.260 --> 37:23.590
your temper sometimes.

37:24.940 --> 37:26.170
When you two are out there,

37:26.170 --> 37:28.030
you should be patient with each other.

37:28.030 --> 37:29.010
Neither of you should feel

37:29.010 --> 37:31.270
that you are the one who suffers the most.

37:37.360 --> 37:39.320
You'll know
when you meet him in the future.

37:39.320 --> 37:40.510
He's the kind of person

37:40.510 --> 37:42.500
who will never make you
throw a temper tantrum.

37:42.500 --> 37:44.030
When will you bring him back

37:44.150 --> 37:45.280
for me to take a look?

37:47.960 --> 37:49.420
Why are you in such a hurry?

37:49.840 --> 37:50.970
I'm not rushing you.

37:51.980 --> 37:53.000
Whether you rush it

37:53.000 --> 37:53.920
or take your time,

37:53.920 --> 37:55.780
your life is yours to live anyway.

37:57.710 --> 37:58.630
I'm just

38:00.550 --> 38:01.810
looking forward to it.

38:07.630 --> 38:09.400
Zhuang Zhuang, Madam Zhuang!

38:09.800 --> 38:11.800
I'm here to wish you a Happy New Year!

38:18.350 --> 38:19.710
Why bother doing this?

38:20.070 --> 38:21.270
It's what I should do.

38:21.420 --> 38:22.280
Here, Mrs. Qin.

38:23.480 --> 38:25.210
Little Zhuang Zhuang, come on.

38:26.800 --> 38:27.730
No need for that.

38:27.980 --> 38:30.150
-What are you doing, Qin?
-Is this a dessert from Beijing?

38:30.150 --> 38:31.130
Let me try it.

38:31.420 --> 38:32.030
Come on.

38:32.110 --> 38:33.170
What are you doing?

38:33.420 --> 38:34.150
Mom, look at her.

38:34.150 --> 38:35.550
She won't even let me eat.

38:37.210 --> 38:38.170
If Zhuang Zhuang won't let you eat,

38:38.170 --> 38:39.300
then just don't eat.

38:39.840 --> 38:41.230
Listen to Zhuang Zhuang.

38:41.230 --> 38:42.490
Right, Zhuang Zhuang?

38:44.400 --> 38:46.690
Shunyin likes you so much.

38:47.050 --> 38:48.540
He told his dad and me.

38:48.610 --> 38:49.410
He said, "Mom,

38:49.630 --> 38:52.050
I even wish I could pluck the stars
from the sky

38:52.050 --> 38:53.850
and give them to Zhuang Zhuang."

38:54.690 --> 38:55.210
Right?

38:56.400 --> 38:58.800
His dad and I like you, too.

38:58.800 --> 39:00.130
Look how pretty you are.

39:00.900 --> 39:01.900
You look exactly like your mom

39:01.900 --> 39:02.570
when she was young.

39:02.570 --> 39:03.150
Right?

39:05.670 --> 39:06.550
Honestly,

39:06.630 --> 39:07.900
his dad and I

39:08.030 --> 39:09.300
have long seen you

39:09.320 --> 39:10.720
as our daughter-in-law.

39:12.880 --> 39:14.170
Still pouting?

39:14.920 --> 39:16.250
Zhuang Zhuang, tell me.

39:16.440 --> 39:18.460
Is it that his dad and I didn't do well?

39:18.460 --> 39:19.880
Or is it Shunyin's problem?

39:19.880 --> 39:20.630
Tell us,

39:20.730 --> 39:21.940
and we'll change. Is that okay?

39:21.940 --> 39:22.840
Yes, I'll change.

39:22.840 --> 39:23.320
Qin...

39:23.360 --> 39:23.890
Mrs. Qin.

39:25.110 --> 39:26.460
Mrs. Qin, you and your husband

39:26.460 --> 39:27.670
really helped me a lot.

39:27.670 --> 39:28.630
I really appreciate it.

39:28.630 --> 39:29.130
Actually,

39:29.130 --> 39:31.380
I should've been the one
going to visit you for the New Year.

39:31.380 --> 39:32.570
It's New Year's Eve.

39:32.590 --> 39:34.520
Everyone's in good spirits today.

39:34.530 --> 39:36.760
There's something I really shouldn't say.

39:36.760 --> 39:37.210
Why...

39:37.400 --> 39:39.260
Why are we
bringing this up again?

39:39.630 --> 39:41.900
Didn't we make a fuss
about this last year?

39:41.900 --> 39:42.570
When

39:42.570 --> 39:43.800
will this ever end?

39:44.530 --> 39:45.980
You're absolutely right.

39:45.980 --> 39:47.740
You young people are

39:47.940 --> 39:49.590
together one day, breaking up the next,

39:49.590 --> 39:50.790
always making a fuss.

39:50.800 --> 39:51.860
Wouldn't that be great if you two

39:51.860 --> 39:53.260
just be together nicely?

39:53.610 --> 39:55.420
Actually, let me be honest with you.

39:55.420 --> 39:57.090
Our colleagues, friends,

39:57.090 --> 39:57.890
and relatives

39:58.010 --> 40:00.480
all know you two are
going to register for marriage.

40:00.480 --> 40:02.320
His father and I are even preparing

40:02.320 --> 40:04.080
to organize your wedding.

40:04.170 --> 40:05.670
Why are you throwing a tantrum

40:05.670 --> 40:06.550
and wanting to break up?

40:06.550 --> 40:07.530
You can't break up.

40:07.530 --> 40:08.350
If you do...

40:08.800 --> 40:10.130
If you break up, I'll...

40:10.260 --> 40:12.560
I'll be so embarrassed.

40:12.710 --> 40:15.600
Qin, that's in the past.

40:16.010 --> 40:17.210
Why bring it up again?

40:17.610 --> 40:18.890
Yeah, Mrs. Qin.

40:19.090 --> 40:21.590
And what do you mean
by "register for marriage"?

40:21.590 --> 40:23.200
I never agreed to that.

40:23.320 --> 40:23.860
Besides, we were

40:23.860 --> 40:25.520
never even in a relationship.

40:25.550 --> 40:26.510
What do you mean by breaking up

40:26.510 --> 40:27.500
and getting back together?

40:27.500 --> 40:28.230
And those...

40:28.800 --> 40:30.400
Those rumors among the relatives,

40:30.400 --> 40:31.660
didn't your family...

40:33.210 --> 40:33.960
Didn't your family

40:33.960 --> 40:35.460
spread them yourselves, Mrs. Qin?

40:35.460 --> 40:36.190
I hope you

40:36.190 --> 40:37.000
won't use such words

40:37.000 --> 40:38.800
to guilt-trip us anymore, okay?

40:39.110 --> 40:40.240
That's a bit harsh.

40:40.650 --> 40:42.710
How would we dare guilt-trip you?

40:45.480 --> 40:46.540
Then let me ask you.

40:46.960 --> 40:47.840
Tell me,

40:48.500 --> 40:50.590
what exactly is wrong with Shunyin?

40:50.930 --> 40:51.480
Qin.

40:52.550 --> 40:53.090
Let's not

40:53.090 --> 40:55.290
interfere in the kids' business, okay?

40:58.740 --> 41:00.510
Let me say something.

41:01.590 --> 41:03.360
Let me guess, Zhuang Zhuang.

41:03.980 --> 41:05.290
You went to Beijing

41:05.610 --> 41:07.270
and broadened your horizons,

41:07.420 --> 41:08.950
so you look down on Shunyin.

41:09.510 --> 41:10.310
Is that right?

41:10.780 --> 41:11.640
Let me tell you.

41:11.670 --> 41:12.470
In this world,

41:12.690 --> 41:14.070
Shunyin is the man

41:14.110 --> 41:15.240
who treats you best.

41:15.920 --> 41:16.940
Plus, your parents and I are

41:16.940 --> 41:18.260
such good friends.

41:18.440 --> 41:20.000
Really, you can't dump him.

41:20.000 --> 41:20.920
You really can't.

41:20.920 --> 41:22.610
You can't shake off this responsibility.

41:22.610 --> 41:23.980
If you do, you...

41:24.070 --> 41:25.470
I... I'm not a liability.

41:26.940 --> 41:28.000
I'm a super glue!

41:28.070 --> 41:28.760
I'll stick to her

41:28.760 --> 41:29.690
and peel off a layer of her skin.

41:29.690 --> 41:30.340
You know?

41:31.070 --> 41:31.650
Kang.

41:33.280 --> 41:34.380
What are you saying?

41:34.380 --> 41:34.860
I...

41:36.130 --> 41:36.900
Are you

41:37.010 --> 41:38.500
trying to harm our Zhuang Zhuang?

41:38.500 --> 41:39.420
No, no, Mom.

41:39.500 --> 41:40.570
No, well...

41:41.260 --> 41:41.690
Mrs. Zhuang,

41:41.690 --> 41:42.340
I mean,

41:42.500 --> 41:43.980
I would tear off a layer of my own skin.

41:43.980 --> 41:45.130
You just have to push me, don't you?

41:45.130 --> 41:45.460
No.

41:45.530 --> 41:46.980
How am I pushing you?

41:48.860 --> 41:49.320
Fine.

41:50.110 --> 41:50.550
Then let's just

41:50.550 --> 41:51.750
talk this over today.

41:53.980 --> 41:55.070
Mrs. Qin, honestly,

41:55.070 --> 41:56.920
I didn't want to fall out
with anyone today.

41:56.920 --> 41:59.120
But if you insist on acting like this...

42:00.590 --> 42:02.520
Are you going to say it, or should I?

42:03.980 --> 42:04.670
I... I...

42:05.550 --> 42:07.070
I'll say it.

42:07.090 --> 42:09.050
I... I love you very much.

42:11.480 --> 42:11.920
Fine.

42:13.720 --> 42:14.340
Mrs. Qin.

42:14.820 --> 42:16.840
Kang Shunyin once went to Beijing
to find me

42:16.840 --> 42:17.780
and turned my place

42:17.780 --> 42:18.880
upside down.

42:19.130 --> 42:20.130
He also stalked me

42:20.510 --> 42:21.380
and even hit my friend

42:21.380 --> 42:22.380
with a motorbike.

42:23.980 --> 42:25.180
When did this happen?

42:25.230 --> 42:26.010
Who did he hit?

42:26.010 --> 42:26.780
Was it serious?

42:26.780 --> 42:27.320
Wait, well...

42:27.320 --> 42:28.550
Why didn't you tell us?

42:28.550 --> 42:29.810
Zhuang Zhuang, you...

42:29.840 --> 42:30.610
Don't talk nonsense.

42:30.610 --> 42:32.110
I didn't hit anyone. If I did,

42:32.110 --> 42:33.840
I'd have been... arrested long ago.

42:33.840 --> 42:34.980
Then come to the police station with me.

42:34.980 --> 42:36.420
Zhuang Zhuang, why talk about going

42:36.420 --> 42:38.420
to the police station during the New Year?

42:38.420 --> 42:39.380
Even now, you...

42:39.650 --> 42:40.500
You're still defending that man.

42:40.500 --> 42:42.430
I told you I did catch you cheating.

42:42.550 --> 42:43.110
Don't you dare...

42:43.110 --> 42:44.110
What are you talking about?

42:44.110 --> 42:45.040
What? Cheating?

42:45.110 --> 42:46.690
Get out. Both of you, get out.

42:46.690 --> 42:47.230
No, I didn't...

42:47.230 --> 42:47.880
How dare you make

42:47.880 --> 42:48.570
false accusations here?

42:48.570 --> 42:49.070
No, well...

42:49.070 --> 42:51.030
Zhuang Zhuang already rejected you
a long time ago.

42:51.030 --> 42:52.410
Who she is with now is

42:53.010 --> 42:54.630
none of your business!
